WELCOME TO BIG FIVE COUNTRY!
Situated in the South-Eastern corner of the Manyeleti Game reserve, close to the unfenced borders of Sabi Sand and Kruger National Park, lies our exclusive camp that offers unparalleled game viewing in the heart of big five country!
Offering an authentic bush experience, our camp achieves a balance between comfort and bushveld ambiance.
#justgo #travel #travelpic #africa #safari

WELCOME TO ZANZIBAR
Zanzibar has become the number one honeymoon destination in East Africa. It is a wonderful island, with classic tropical beaches, lush plantations, an incredible history and a fascinating culture.
Apart from historic Stone Town, with its labyrinth of narrow streets, Zanzibar is known for its beautiful palm-fringed beaches and pristine coral reefs. One of our more affordable options includes 7 nights in a 4 star boutique hotel on the East coast of Zanzibar. The boutique hotel has a central reception area, a pool just a few steps from the sand and a beachfront bar which serves a full range of drinks and cocktails throughout the day. The open sided restaurant with its position on the beachfront provides uninterrupted views of the ocean.

WELCOME TO BOTSWANA
JustGo can tailor a Safari trip to your individual needs. Included in our offer is a fully kitted Land Cruiser for your ultimate adventure.
From our personal experience, we recommend a 10 Day safari including Makgadikgadi pans, Okavango Delta, Moremi game reserve, Savuti, and Chobe. Botswana is a very user friendly country for first time overlanders, and with the right equipment and preparation ‚Äì all supplied by us ‚Äì you will only need to bring your sense of adventure!

WELCOME TO THE OKAVANGO
For a unique African safari holiday, take a private-guided safari into top wildlife areas such as Moremi, Savuti, and Chobe.
Each authentic mobile tented safari is tailor-made to guest‚Äôs preferences and time frame. We offer luxury camping in some of the best wilderness areas, providing spacious 3m x 3m dome tents with en-suite bush shower and toilet, including all bedding.
